title: Honor Rewards?
body: So it seems that I don't have my ward skin for my honor level, but my friends seem to have received theirs about a week ago. Is it just coming along a little slower for me?

replies.body: Some of these rewards are just getting delayed a little is all. If you still don't see yours in about a week or so be sure to shoot us a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so you don't get missed!
